<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Yes all humans are, however systemic racism has existed for hundreds of years and White people have always had the power to change this. Those charact<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Yes all humans are, however systemic racism has existed for hundreds of years and White people have always had the power to change this. Those characteristics that you are questioning are more importantly probed in this book in relation to the racism in the world (that still exists today) .<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
