<span id="freeTextContainer13486350679608773432">This book made me ache inside. Hughes is an excellent writer and his stories are like razor blades that draw fine little lines in your heart. You don&apos;t even realize you&apos;re bleeding until it&apos;s done. </span>
  <span id="freeText13486350679608773432" style="display:none">This book made me ache inside. Hughes is an excellent writer and his stories are like razor blades that draw fine little lines in your heart. You don't even realize you're bleeding until it's done. </span>
