  <div class="friendReviews elementListBrown" >
    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_686935912" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/686935912" />
    <a title="Matthew" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/9456564-matthew"><img alt="Matthew" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1336770237p2/9456564.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/686935912?book_show_action=true">Aug 05, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Matthew" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Matthew" href="/user/show/9456564-matthew">Matthew</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer686935912" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12451011841870209741">It&apos;s hard not to love every bit of Langston Hughes&apos;s contribution to American letters. Although best know as a poet, I greatly admire his prose too. Two other prose works of his to check out are two of my favorite works of American memoir: &quot;The Big Sea&quot; and &quot;I Wonder as I Wander.&quot;</span>
  <span id="freeText12451011841870209741" style="display:none">It's hard not to love every bit of Langston Hughes's contribution to American letters. Although best know as a poet, I greatly admire his prose too. Two other prose works of his to check out are two of my favorite works of American memoir: "The Big Sea" and "I Wonder as I Wander."</span>
  <a data-text-id="12451011841870209741" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


