<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer5256989459144433570">James Mercer Langston Hughes was an American poet, social activist, novelist, playwright, short story writer, and columnist. He was one of the earliest innovators of the then-new literary art form jazz poetry. Hughes is best known for his work during the Harlem Renaissance. He famously wrote about the period that &quot;Harlem was in vogue.&quot;</span>
  <span id="freeText5256989459144433570" style="display:none">James Mercer Langston Hughes was an American poet, social activist, novelist, playwright, short story writer, and columnist. He was one of the earliest innovators of the then-new literary art form jazz poetry. Hughes is best known for his work during the Harlem Renaissance. He famously wrote about the period that "Harlem was in vogue."</span>
  <a data-text-id="5256989459144433570" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

